thread.title: Mark

author: Mark
title: Mark
text: Ordered a pair of OR Helium rain pants to be delivered to the USA. When placing order, the status was they were in stock and would be delivered by 3/7/17 to 3/13/17. I placed the order on 2/14/17 and they were delivered on 3/14/17, four weeks. I did not need to contact their customer service so do not know how smoothly that goes. I am completely satisfied with the product and the service I received from Trekkinn.
